<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Page Not Found - Lush Scents</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    
    body {
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      color: #333;
    }
    
    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px 10%;
      background-color: white;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    
    .logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      padding: 5px 15px;
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 30px;
    }
    
    .nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .nav a:hover {
      color: #ff6b6b;
    }
    
    .icons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    
    .icons a {
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .main-content {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 70vh;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 50px 10%;
    }
    
    .content-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 30px;
      max-width: 800px;
    }
    
    .perfume-image {
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      border-radius: 50%;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .perfume-bottle {
      width: 80px;
      height: 140px;
      background-color: #333;
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 20px 20px;
    }
    
    .perfume-bottle:before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -20px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 40px;
      height: 20px;
      background-color: #222;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    
    .perfume-bottle:after {
      content: '404';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      color: #ff6b6b;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .title {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #777;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .btn {
      background-color: #000;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #ff6b6b;
    }
    
    .suggestions {
      margin-top: 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .suggestions h3 {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .suggestions h3:after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -20px;
      top: 50%;
      width: 10px;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: #ff6b6b;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
    }
    
    .suggestion-links {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .suggestion-links a {
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .suggestion-links a:hover {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      border-color: #ccc;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .header {
        padding: 15px 5%;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 15px;
      }
      
      .main-content {
        padding: 30px 5%;
      }
      
      .title {
        font-size: 36px;
      }
      
      .suggestion-links {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%-include('../../views/partials/user/header')%>

  
  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="perfume-image">
        <div class="perfume-bottle"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-content">
        <h1 class="title">Scent Not Found</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">The fragrance you're looking for seems to have evaporated.</p>
        <p>Don't worry, we have many other captivating scents waiting for you in our collection.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">BACK TO HOME</a>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
<%-include('../../views/partials/user/footer')%>
